  <!-- EN: ever growing -->
  <VRE_EverGrowing.label>不断成长</VRE_EverGrowing.label>
  <!-- EN: Carriers of this gene do not stop growing until they reach a biological age of 60. They will keep increasing in size, reaching gargantuan sizes.\n\nAs they grow, they will become slower, but also stagger-immune. With size, their health pool will also increase. -->
  <VRE_EverGrowing.description>这种基因的携带者直到生物年龄满60岁前，体型都会不断成长下去。他们的身体部件耐久度将随之提高，然而移动速度也会随之降低。</VRE_EverGrowing.description>
  
</LanguageData>